name: Verify that field Employee Leasing Policy Typ is defaulted to 'Non-Employee Leasing Policy'

testSteps.description: Given underwriter selects 'Workers Compensation' from create quote tile

And field EmployeeLeasingPolicyType dropdown option has
| Non-Employee Leasing Policy |
| Employee Leasing Policy |
| Employee Leasing Policy for Non-Leased Workers |
| Employee Leasing Policy - Client Company for Leased Workers of Client Company |
| Employee Leasing Policy - Client Company for Leased Workers of a Single Client Company |
| Employee Leasing Policy for Non-Leased Workers of Client Company |
| Employee Leasing Policy for Leased and Non-Leased Workers of Client Company |
Then field EmployeeLeasingPolicyType should be defaulted to 'Non-Employee Leasing Policy'
